title: HERE'S LUCY -- Lucy's Big Break ( Fifth Season Premiere )
description:
Lucille Ball injured her leg not doing a TV stunt, but during a skiing accident between seasons.  It was decided to have her character Lucy Carter recovering following the same fate, and that last several episodes which should be seen in order. So I've labelled some of those files with "broken leg # .... "

Guest Stars -- Lloyd Bridges, Mary Wickes, and Alan Oppenheimer
